                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5635" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0857</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9435 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“灯塔”引航，“哨兵”列位：交控科技自主创新战略引领下的智能风控体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Beacon &amp; Sentry”: TCT’s Construction of Risk Management System under the Guidance of Independent Innovation Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">崔永梅，杨婷羽，王欣欣，李瑞，郜春海，苟娟琼，应文池</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交控科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业风险管理（COSO-ERM，2017）；组织变革；内部控制；大数据治理；自主创新型企业；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Enterprise Risk Management; Organizational Innovation; Internal Control; Big Data Governance; Independent Innovation Enterprise</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">这是一个瞬息万变的时代，是一个波涛汹涌的时代——中国企业越来越认识到自己正跨入VUCA时代。面对易变性、不确定性、复杂性和模糊性共存的内、外部生存环境，如何采取更为智能的策略进行风险管理，成为当前自主创新型企业发展所面临的重要难题。本案例根据第一手的访谈和实地调研资料，聚焦城市轨道交通信号领域的龙头——交控科技，概括公司在风险管理智能化转型过程中的成效与经验，描述其在德鲁克“灯塔”理论的指引下，如何将风险意识融入企业战略与文化，通过BU虚拟组织、区域铁三角、四板斧的变革和总裁驾驶舱的落地，进行更为灵活、精准的风险管理，为其他面临“卡脖子”难题的自主创新型企业如何增强组织韧性、结合大数据技术转型公司风险管理体系、提高企业的风险应对能力、增强长期竞争力提供了借鉴和经验。本案例适用于企业管理中有关全面风险管理的问题，旨在帮助学员掌握最新版本COSO-ERM框架要义，以及启发学员对自主创新型企业搭建智能风控体系的深入探讨。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This is an era of rapid change- Chinese enterprises are increasingly aware that they are stepping into the VUCA era. Facing the internal and external environment of Volatility, Uncertainty, Complexity and Ambiguity, the awareness of enterprise risk management is gradually enhanced. How to make risk management activities more intelligent has become an important matter for the development of technological innovation enterprises. Based on the first-hand research and field interview data, this case focuses on Traffic Control Technology Co., Ltd. (TCT) --the leader in the signal field of urban rail transit--summarizes TCT&#39;s achievements and experience in the process of intelligent transformation of risk management, and describes how it integrates risk awareness into corporate strategy and culture under the guidance of Peter F.Drucker Academy’s “Beacon” theory, Through the innovation of organization of BU, Regional Iron Triangle and Four Axe and the landing of the President&#39;s Cockpit, more flexible and accurate risk management can be carried out in TCT. This case provides experience for other independent innovation companies to to combine big data technology and risk management system, to improve business performance and the enterprise&#39;s risk response ability, and enhance long-term competitiveness. This case is applicable to the problems of risk management and organizational innovation in enterprise management. It aims to help students master the essentials of COSO-ERM theory, and inspire students to deeply explore the construction of intelligent risk management system in technology-innovative enterprises. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》、《管理会计》、《会计学》、《审计学》、《大数据与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业战略转型、文化升级与组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
